snippet.title: Mariano Chicho Frumboli & Juana Sepulveda, Milonga LAX January 18, 2014
snippet.description:
music: Milonga Para Una Armonica by Beltango
http://LivingTango.com/milonga-lax
 
Sorry but the camera was not functioning right in the super dim light, this is all we got...better than nothing. However watching them perform live was absolutely breathtaking. Can't wait to have them come back to LA in 2015!
